
=render layout: 'field_wrapper' do
  .form-check
    =f.check_box :allow_in_iframe, class: 'form-check-input'
    =f.label :allow_in_iframe, 'Allow inside an iframe', class: 'form-check-label'
  .form-text
    Removes the <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/X-Frame-Options"
    style="text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">X-Frame-Options header</a>.
